Package rs.edu.raf.test.exception

Provides the exceptions that can occur while importing a Test from a JSON or XML file.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidXMLQuestionNode
    Exception indicating that a question defined in XML has an invalid node.
    NoQuestionTextException
    Exception indicating that a question attempting to be imported doesn't have a valid text defined.
    NullQuestionTypeJsonException
    Exception indicating that a question defined in a JSON file doesn't have a type value defined.
